.TH SINGINE-MAN 1 "2026-03-16" "singine 0.2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
singine-man \- open Singine manpages by topic
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B singine man
[\fITOPIC\fR] [\fB--raw\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Opens a manpage from Singine's bundled manual set. Without a topic, the main
.BR singine (1)
page is opened.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --raw
Print the filesystem path to the selected manpage instead of opening it with
.BR man (1).
.SH TOPICS
.TP
.B singine
Top-level command index and AI conversation data quick-start.
.TP
.B singine-ai
Governed AI session recording, permission tracking, and conversation-data
centralisation for Claude, Codex, and OpenAI.
Start here if you want to list, inspect, export, or centralise AI conversation
data.
.TP
.B singine-bridge
SQLite and JDBC bridge operations. Covers how to build the bridge, run SPARQL
queries, and query AI session data once it has been synced.
.TP
.B singine-policy
AI policy pack management: template, canonify, sync, evaluate, approve, report.
Covers the relationship between policy records and session permission records.
.TP
.B singine-decide
Governance decision requests. Covers online and offline (JSON fallback) modes.
Use this to register a decision against a completed AI session.
.TP
.B singine-context
Terminal context inspection and sourced environment.
.TP
.B singine-runtime
Runtime capability inspection and wrapped-command execution.
.TP
.B singine-model
Singine model objects and bridge surfaces.
.TP
.B singine-activity
Activity taxonomy: list, inspect, run, score. Covers DP(DP) meta-activities.
.TP
.B singine-jdbc-url
Print the JDBC URL for a bridge database.
.TP
.B singine-xml
XML matrix and artefact generation.
.TP
.B singine-auth
Authentication bootstrap and TOTP login.
.TP
.B singine-idp
Identity provider operations.
.TP
.B singine-install
Launcher and manpage installation.
.TP
.B singine-singe
Governed identity rendering from @mentions.
.TP
.B singine-find
Filesystem path discovery via the
.I filesAboutTopic
activity.
.TP
.B singine-mv
Move filesystem paths from stdin into a destination directory.
.TP
.B singine-transfer
File transfer and queue/stack helpers.
.TP
.B singine-smtp
SMTP test and send helpers.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
# Top-level index (start here).
singine man

# AI conversation data — listing, inspection, export, centralisation.
singine man singine-ai

# Semantic bridge and SPARQL queries over AI session data.
singine man singine-bridge

# Policy governance for Claude, Codex, and OpenAI.
singine man singine-policy

# Governance decision records (online and offline).
singine man singine-decide

# Runtime, context, and execution envelope.
singine man singine-runtime
singine man singine-context

# Activity taxonomy and DP(DP).
singine man singine-activity

# Get the raw filesystem path to a manpage.
singine man singine-auth --raw
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR singine (1),
.BR singine-ai (1),
.BR singine-bridge (1),
.BR singine-policy (1)
